{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.1","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:1","prev_osis_id":"Jas.001.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019acception de personnes condamn\u00e9e<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. (L\u00e9 19:15. De 25:13-15. Ps 82. Ac 10:34, 35.) (Ro 13:8-10. Mt 5:7, 19; 7:1, 2, 12.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Mes fr\u00e8res, que votre foi en notre glorieux Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ soit exempte de toute acception de personnes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.2","name":"Jacques 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.1.27","name":"Jacques 1:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.1.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.2","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:2","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Supposez, en effet, qu\u2019il entre dans votre assembl\u00e9e un homme avec un anneau d\u2019or et un habit magnifique, et qu\u2019il y entre aussi un pauvre mis\u00e9rablement v\u00eatu;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.3","name":"Jacques 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.1","name":"Jacques 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.3","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:3","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>si, tournant vos regards vers celui qui porte l\u2019habit magnifique, vous lui dites: Toi, assieds-toi ici \u00e0 cette place d\u2019honneur! Et si vous dites au pauvre: Toi, tiens-toi l\u00e0 debout! Ou bien: Assieds-toi au-dessous de mon marchepied!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.4","name":"Jacques 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.2","name":"Jacques 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.4","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:4","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>ne faites-vous pas en vous-m\u00eames une distinction, et ne jugez-vous pas sous l\u2019inspiration de pens\u00e9es mauvaises?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.5","name":"Jacques 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.3","name":"Jacques 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.5","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:5","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\u00c9coutez, mes fr\u00e8res bien-aim\u00e9s: Dieu n\u2019a-t-il pas choisi les pauvres aux yeux du monde, pour qu\u2019ils soient riches en la foi, et h\u00e9ritiers du royaume qu\u2019il a promis \u00e0 ceux qui l\u2019aiment?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.6","name":"Jacques 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.4","name":"Jacques 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.6","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:6","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et vous, vous avilissez le pauvre! Ne sont-ce pas les riches qui vous oppriment, et qui vous tra\u00eenent devant les tribunaux?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.7","name":"Jacques 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.5","name":"Jacques 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.7","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:7","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ne sont-ce pas eux qui outragent le beau nom que vous portez?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.8","name":"Jacques 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.6","name":"Jacques 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.8","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:8","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Si vous accomplissez la loi royale, selon l\u2019\u00c9criture: Tu aimeras ton prochain comme toi-m\u00eame, vous faites bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.9","name":"Jacques 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.7","name":"Jacques 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.9","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:9","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mais si vous faites acception de personnes, vous commettez un p\u00e9ch\u00e9, vous \u00eates condamn\u00e9s par la loi comme des transgresseurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.10","name":"Jacques 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.8","name":"Jacques 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.10","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:10","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Car quiconque observe toute la loi, mais p\u00e8che contre un seul commandement, devient coupable de tous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.11","name":"Jacques 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.9","name":"Jacques 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.11","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:11","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>En effet, celui qui a dit: Tu ne commettras point d\u2019adult\u00e8re, a dit aussi: Tu ne tueras point. Or, si tu ne commets point d\u2019adult\u00e8re, mais que tu commettes un meurtre, tu deviens transgresseur de la loi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.12","name":"Jacques 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.10","name":"Jacques 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.12","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:12","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Parlez et agissez comme devant \u00eatre jug\u00e9s par une loi de libert\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.13","name":"Jacques 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.11","name":"Jacques 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.13","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:13","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>car le jugement est sans mis\u00e9ricorde pour qui n\u2019a pas fait mis\u00e9ricorde. La mis\u00e9ricorde triomphe du jugement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.14","name":"Jacques 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.12","name":"Jacques 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.14","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:14","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La foi sans les \u0153uvres<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-26: cf. (Ga 5:6. Ja 1:22-27. Mt 7:21-27.) H\u00e9 11:17-19, 31. 1 Jn 2:3-6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>\n    Mes fr\u00e8res, que sert-il \u00e0 quelqu\u2019un de dire qu\u2019il a la foi, s\u2019il n\u2019a pas les \u0153uvres? La foi peut-elle le sauver?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.15","name":"Jacques 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.13","name":"Jacques 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.15","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:15","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Si un fr\u00e8re ou une s\u0153ur sont nus et manquent de la nourriture de chaque jour,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.16","name":"Jacques 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.14","name":"Jacques 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.16","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:16","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>et que l\u2019un d\u2019entre vous leur dise: Allez en paix, chauffez-vous et vous rassasiez! Et que vous ne leur donniez pas ce qui est n\u00e9cessaire au corps, \u00e0 quoi cela sert-il?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.17","name":"Jacques 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.15","name":"Jacques 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.17","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:17","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il en est ainsi de la foi: si elle n\u2019a pas les \u0153uvres, elle est morte en elle-m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.18","name":"Jacques 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.16","name":"Jacques 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.18","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:18","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mais quelqu\u2019un dira: Toi, tu as la foi; et moi, j\u2019ai les \u0153uvres. Montre-moi ta foi sans les \u0153uvres, et moi, je te montrerai la foi par mes \u0153uvres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.19","name":"Jacques 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.17","name":"Jacques 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.19","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:19","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Tu crois qu\u2019il y a un seul Dieu, tu fais bien; les d\u00e9mons le croient aussi, et ils tremblent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.20","name":"Jacques 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.18","name":"Jacques 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.20","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:20","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Veux-tu savoir, \u00f4 homme vain, que la foi sans les \u0153uvres est inutile?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.21","name":"Jacques 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.19","name":"Jacques 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.21","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:21","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Abraham, notre p\u00e8re, ne fut-il pas justifi\u00e9 par les \u0153uvres, lorsqu\u2019il offrit son fils Isaac sur l\u2019autel?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.22","name":"Jacques 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.20","name":"Jacques 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.22","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:22","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Tu vois que la foi agissait avec ses \u0153uvres, et que par les \u0153uvres la foi fut rendue parfaite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.23","name":"Jacques 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.21","name":"Jacques 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.23","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:23","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ainsi s\u2019accomplit ce que dit l\u2019\u00c9criture: Abraham crut \u00e0 Dieu, et cela lui fut imput\u00e9 \u00e0 justice; et il fut appel\u00e9 ami de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.24","name":"Jacques 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.22","name":"Jacques 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.24","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:24","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Vous voyez que l\u2019homme est justifi\u00e9 par les \u0153uvres, et non par la foi seulement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.25","name":"Jacques 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.23","name":"Jacques 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.25","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:25","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.002.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Rahab la prostitu\u00e9e ne fut-elle pas \u00e9galement justifi\u00e9e par les \u0153uvres, lorsqu\u2019elle re\u00e7ut les messagers et qu\u2019elle les fit partir par un autre chemin?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.26","name":"Jacques 2:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.24","name":"Jacques 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.26","label":"","reference":"Jacques 2:26","prev_osis_id":"Jas.002.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.2.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Comme le corps sans \u00e2me est mort, de m\u00eame la foi sans les \u0153uvres est morte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.2","name":"Jacques 2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.3.1","name":"Jacques 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.2.25","name":"Jacques 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.2.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudf